<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/17(Sat.) Copyright Issues &amp; How to speak so that people want to listen (Host:Shuman)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=524&amp;p=547#p547"><![CDATA[
7/17(Sat.) Copyright Issues &amp; How to speak so that people want to listen (Host:Shuman)<br /><br />Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw#success">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw#success</a><!-- m --><br /><br />會議 ID:929 8726 6213<br />密碼:112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.<br /><br />Session1: 7 Copyright Issues<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bidsketch.com/blog/everything-else/copyright-issues/">https://www.bidsketch.com/blog/everythi ... ht-issues/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.How much information do you know about copyright?<br />2.Have you ever touched the red line of copyright?<br />3.Create is difficult. How to protect our copyrights?<br />4.Fake items are everywhere. Can you make some example?<br /><br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session2: How to speak so that people want to listen<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dEkEAFaV818">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dEkEAFaV818</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.Do you know how do speak so that people want to listen?<br />2.Do you know how to make a conversation interesting?<br />3.How can we improve our speaking skill?<br />4.Have ever heard or joined some speaking courses?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Sat Jul 10, 2021 8:44 pm</p><hr />
